7033   // A boolean compared to true/false can be simplified to Op0/true/false in
7034   // 14 out of the 20 (10 predicates * 2 constants) possible combinations.
7035   // Cases not handled by InstSimplify are always 'not' of Op0.
7036   if (match(B, m_Zero())) {
